# {{ project_name }}

AWS Lambda service built with Python and AWS CDK.

## Setup

```bash
make dev       # Create venv & install dependencies
```

## Development

```bash
make lint      # Lint, format, and spell check
make test      # Run all tests
make build     # Build Lambda package
```

## Deploy

```bash
make deploy                       # Deploy all stacks
make deploy-monitoring-dashboard  # Deploy monitoring only
make destroy                      # Tear down all stacks
```

## Logs

```bash
ENVIRONMENT=dev LAMBDA=hello_lambda make logs
```

## Project Structure

- `service/` — Lambda application code (handlers, models, logic)
- `infrastructure/` — CDK stacks (Lambda, monitoring)
- `tests/` — Infrastructure and service tests

Run `make help` for all available commands.
